{"id":3680,"date":"2023-06-13T19:00:33","date_gmt":"2023-06-13T19:00:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/?post_type=mpa_location&#038;p=3680"},"modified":"2023-09-29T07:43:44","modified_gmt":"2023-09-29T07:43:44","slug":"greece","status":"publish","type":"mpa_location","link":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/location\/greece\/","title":{"rendered":"Greece"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section alignfull alignfull\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__wrapper getwid-padding-top-none\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background-holder\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background\"><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__foreground\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-content\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-style-wide-space is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-advanced-heading\" style=\"margin-bottom:30px\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-advanced-heading__content\">Description<\/h3><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to Greece, a country steeped in ancient history, adorned with breathtaking landscapes, and renowned for its warm hospitality. From the iconic ruins of Athens to the stunning islands of Santorini and Crete, Greece offers a truly captivating experience for travelers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-default has-color-4-background-color has-background\">\n<p>Traveling is a journey of the soul, a passport to new experiences and perspectives. It opens our hearts, broadens our minds, and reminds us that the world is a tapestry of wonders waiting to be explored.<\/p>\n<cite>John Doue, CEO \u201cLorenty\u201d<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Begin your journey in Athens, the birthplace of democracy. Explore the iconic Acropolis, where the Parthenon stands as a testament to the ancient civilization of Greece. Stroll through the charming streets of Plaka, filled with vibrant shops and traditional tavernas. Immerse yourself in the rich history of the city at the Acropolis Museum, where ancient artifacts come to life.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-rounded-corners\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"866\" height=\"540\" src=\"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/58\/2023\/06\/post-content-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3732\" srcset=\"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/58\/2023\/06\/post-content-4.jpg 866w, https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/58\/2023\/06\/post-content-4-300x187.jpg 300w, https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/58\/2023\/06\/post-content-4-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With its ancient ruins, pristine beaches, and warm Mediterranean climate, Greece offers a perfect blend of history, culture, and natural beauty. Whether you\u2019re exploring archaeological sites, island hopping, or simply unwinding under the Mediterranean sun, Greece will enchant you with its timeless allure and leave you with memories that will last a lifetime.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:550px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section is-style-rounded-corners getwid-margin-tablet-top-medium\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__wrapper\" style=\"padding-top:38px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-left:30px;padding-right:28px\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background-holder\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background ha